# 📘 Changelog

All notable changes and progress made to this project will be documented in this file.

---

## [1.0.0] - 2025-07-12

### 🚀 Initial Project Release

- ✅ Added raw dataset `bank-full.csv` to the repository
- ✅ Launched Jupyter Notebook `decision_tree.ipynb` on Google Colab
- ✅ Imported essential libraries (pandas, sklearn, matplotlib)

---

## [1.1.0] - 2025-07-12

### 🔧 Data Preprocessing

- 🔍 Identified and replaced `'unknown'` values with `NaN`
- 🧹 Filled missing values with `0` for model compatibility
- ✅ Added custom column `Age group` for demographic analysis

---

## [1.2.0] - 2025-07-12

### 📊 Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA)

- 📈 Analyzed relationship between:
  - `Balance` and `Subscription`
  - `Age group` and `Subscription`
- 🧾 Used value counts, groupby, and bar plots for insights

---

## [1.3.0] - 2025-07-12

### 🤖 Model Building

- ✅ Built a `DecisionTreeClassifier` using `scikit-learn`
- ✅ Handled NaNs in `X_train` and `y_train`
- ✅ Split dataset into training and test sets (80/20)

---

## [1.4.0] - 2025-07-12

### ✅ Model Evaluation & Results

- 📊 Evaluated model using `accuracy_score` and `classification_report`
- 💾 Saved predictions to `predictions.csv` for review
- 🌳 Visualized the top 3 levels of the decision tree

---

## [1.5.0] - 2025-07-12

### 🧠 Feature Insights

- 🧪 Calculated feature importances
- 📋 Printed top 10 features influencing prediction
- 🔽 Sorted feature importance values using `numpy`

---

## [1.6.0] - 2025-07-12

### 🧾 Documentation

- 📘 Added `README.md` with full project description, objective, results
- 🗂️ Structured folder layout and file organization
- 📢 Drafted LinkedIn content for sharing project publicly

---

## 📌 Planned for Future

- Export decision tree visualization as an image
- Try pruning or hyperparameter tuning
- Compare with other classifiers (e.g. Random Forest)

---

